{"tid":2208523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中區唐狗頭部意外卡鐵欄獲救","createTime":"2020-09-19T03:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T05:04:01.000Z","uid":41404,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"551d86a2434fd301d51ca6583a07aa25d1d96675","tid":2208523,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T03:49:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=406123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406123&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCiKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=0fb26752\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406123&h=5f192193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=406123</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】一隻唐狗在中區被困路邊鐵欄，愛護動物協會職員將牠救出。<br />\n<br />\n被困的唐狗十多歲，約一米長，頭部卡在鐵欄內。警員通知愛護動物協會，職員用布包裹唐狗，免牠受驚，再用工具剪斷鐵欄將牠救出。"},{"pid":"3ec6160a252c362f415b226888cd4944211a7222","tid":2208523,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"位手足怕唔怕打針"},{"pid":"f63c7c11fa5c7d74aa6c6ec1c6dc63434df1fc8a","tid":2208523,"uid":23684,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T03:51:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"841e7cf8222b8e7c8dd08dcdcb51fbee2f675826","tid":2208523,"uid":155253,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T03:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/DOG-CENTRAL-200919-09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FDOG-CENTRAL-200919-09.jpg&h=589b7ccf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n提問Q1:圖中有多少隻狗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d78b085f3599b09aeb2f3df777d2adcb92f08de","tid":2208523,"uid":13504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"傻狗仔個樣好蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces